Subject: drm/amdgpu: add HDP flush dummy for UVD 6/7
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 996cab955384122848d8132554de43dce0d3c8a2
Patch-mainline: v4.18-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

The UVD firmware doesn't seem to like the HDP flush here.

This worked for years without HDP flush, so just skip it.

